Hello fellow Wikipedians,
I have just added archive links to {{plural:2|one external link|2 external links}} on [[Battle of Darayya (November 2012–March 2013)]]. Please take a moment to review [https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?diff=prev&oldid=707001411 my edit]. If necessary, add {{tlx|cbignore}} after the link to keep me from modifying it. Alternatively, you can add {{tlx|nobots|deny{{=}}InternetArchiveBot}} to keep me off the page altogether.
